OpenScale Load Cell Monitor
Author: Johnny Hamnesj√∂ Olausson
Email: johnny.hamnesjo@chalmers.se
Institution: Chalmers University of Technology
Department: Department of Industrial and Materials Science

This project intends to provide a beautiful interface for precision
weight measurement using Arduino Uno and the FC22 Compression Load Cell. Originally designed for OpenScale.

Designed with weeaboo aesthetic principles emphasizing simplicity,
precision, and mindful interaction with measurement data.

